{"tid":1096352,"cid":13,"subCid":0,"title":"波鞋網stockX問題","createTime":"2019-04-07T15:56:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-08T18:41:31.000Z","uid":83813,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"354784c5b518296cf80225b0b13164b89e21d774","tid":1096352,"uid":83813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T15:56:42.000Z","msg":"想問stockx個網係咪有啲問題？<br />\n申請帳號果陣 <br />\n又話個密碼要有symbols <br />\n大細階英文，數字<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ER0KKsL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FER0KKsL.png&h=b4e9db2a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n到地址啦 <br />\n咁我用paypal嘅 以前eBay<br />\nAmazon都係直接用香港嘅地址<br />\n件貨最後一係叫我去郵局拎<br />\n一係樓下管理處拎fedax包裹<br />\n<br />\n呢個網嘅地址 佢同我轉咗做唔知咩<br />\n我擔心到時人地唔知點寄比我<br />\n對波鞋 好煩惱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd16bbae8cc24d2e7974a199d0eb86f97b335d9e","tid":1096352,"uid":240910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T16:05:47.000Z","msg":"我都係,話地址有問題依家唔俾我買嘢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有冇ching 識整"},{"pid":"fc3ec1e64aec0b7c2ac700b80e811fbf304bf699","tid":1096352,"uid":83813,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"dd16bbae8cc24d2e7974a199d0eb86f97b335d9e","tid":1096352,"uid":240910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T16:05:47.000Z","msg":"我都係,話地址有問題依家唔俾我買嘢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有冇ching 識整"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T16:09:03.000Z","msg":"我係買咗啦 <br />\n唔知佢最後寄唔寄到<br />\n唉 總之貴少少用GOAT算<br />\nStockx好似幾慢幾垃圾"},{"pid":"c37c49f1f32efd9684d797b51cdc594c96490071","tid":1096352,"uid":240910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fc3ec1e64aec0b7c2ac700b80e811fbf304bf699","tid":1096352,"uid":83813,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"dd16bbae8cc24d2e7974a199d0eb86f97b335d9e","tid":1096352,"uid":240910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T16: